    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Pick your <strong>coriander leaves</strong> from their stalks and set aside for garnish</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander stalks</strong> finely</p>",
