            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> to a large bowl with your <strong>mango chutney</strong>, <strong>chopped coriander stalks</strong>, <strong>sultanas</strong> and the juice of half your <strong>lime[s]</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>yoghurt mix</strong></p><p>Once cooked through, add the <strong>chicken </strong>to the yoghurt mix and stir it all together – this is your <strong>creamy coronation chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
