    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the juice of the <strong>remaining lime[s]</strong> with 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>lime dressing</strong></p>",
