    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>crunchy salad</strong> between bowls</p><p>Top with the<strong> creamy coronation chicken</strong> and garnish with the <strong>coriander leaves</strong>, <strong>flaked almonds</strong> and <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
